'Description: LCD Button Latch Program
'************************************

LCDButtonLatch:
  If LCDDisplay = 1 then LCDDisplay[8] = 1 'Override
  If LCDDisplay = 2 then LCDDisplay[8] = 2 'Up Arrow
  If LCDDisplay = 3 then LCDDisplay[8] = 3 'Select
  If LCDDisplay = 4 then LCDDisplay[8] = 4 'Display
  If LCDDisplay = 5 then LCDDisplay[8] = 5 'Down Arrow
  If LCDDisplay = 6 then LCDDisplay[8] = 6 'Enter
  If LCDDisplay = 7 then LCDDisplay[8] = 7 'Password
